casebody.data:
Brian Keith BLACKWELL
v.
Erick A. HOOKS, Secretary of Prisons Cynthia O. Thornton, Administrator I No. 197P17-2 Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 22, 2018 Mr. Brian Keith Blackwell, for Blackwell, Brian Keith Ms. Kathleen N. Bolton, Assistant Attorney General, for State of North Carolina Mr. James R. Woodall, Jr., District Attorney, for State

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 21st of May 2018 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Chatham County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 22nd of May 2018."

Ervin, J. recused
